## What this service does

- exposes HTTP endpoints derived from the uploaded OpenAPI spec
- exposes a Stripe webhook endpoint at `/webhooks/stripe/payment`
- validates and normalizes inbound payloads
- publishes canonical events to Solace topics
- exposes health and metrics endpoints

